384
00:17:17.439 --> 00:17:21.434
These are simple graphs.

385
00:17:21.434 --> 00:17:24.453
These just express a point. 

386
00:17:24.453 --> 00:17:26.630
When showing different 
types of information or 

387
00:17:26.630 --> 00:17:29.227
displaying types of information 
labels don't help. 

388
00:17:29.227 --> 00:17:32.069
When someone's colorblind 
or not able to tell the graph, 

389
00:17:32.069 --> 00:17:33.534
what it is: apples, 
oranges, bananas, 

390
00:17:33.534 --> 00:17:35.600
they would have a hard time
distinguishing between that.

391
00:17:35.600 --> 00:17:39.211
Option B shows, hey you
can use lines or dots, 

392
00:17:39.211 --> 00:17:41.430
or some other 
type of indicator 

393
00:17:41.430 --> 00:17:43.919
of what that information 
