396
00:17:49.735 --> 00:17:53.283
and put the labels 
right on top 

397
00:17:53.283 --> 00:17:55.104
and while the law says, 
if you put the labels on top 

398
00:17:55.104 --> 00:17:57.061
make sure it meets
those requirements 

399
00:17:57.061 --> 00:18:00.720
of the contrast ratio that 
we're talking about, the 4.5:1.

400
00:18:00.720 --> 00:18:02.113
You get the point with this. 

401
00:18:02.113 --> 00:18:04.118
It shows, hey you can 
label this over the top 

402
00:18:04.118 --> 00:18:07.200
and get rid of 
the legend altogether.

403
00:18:07.520 --> 00:18:11.120
This is an extended version of 
what we just saw a second ago.

404
00:18:11.120 --> 00:18:15.410
If you're trying to identify 
colors or an image 

405
00:18:15.410 --> 00:18:17.730
you can put one, two, 
three, four over the top 

406
00:18:17.730 --> 00:18:19.440
and identify with 
