407
00:18:19.440 --> 00:18:24.518
This also helps 
further reinforce 

408
00:18:24.518 --> 00:18:27.479
if someone has 
difficulty seeing. 

409
00:18:29.479 --> 00:18:31.697
Include image and media 
alternatives in your design. 

410
00:18:31.697 --> 00:18:32.867
For example, you might need 

411
00:18:32.867 --> 00:18:34.400
visible links 
to transcripts of audio,

412
00:18:34.400 --> 00:18:37.280
visible links of audio 
described versions of video,

413
00:18:37.280 --> 00:18:39.390
text along with icons 
and graphical buttons, 

414
00:18:39.390 --> 00:18:45.063
captions and descriptions 
for tables or complex graphs. 

415
00:18:45.063 --> 00:18:48.089
Provide controls for content
that starts automatically. 

416
00:18:48.089 --> 00:18:50.983
That's a big one. I always 
have battled this with clients. 

417
00:18:50.983 --> 00:18:52.960
I have a lot of clients 
that want to have

418
00:18:52.960 --> 00:18:56.146
automatic sliders or 
automatic videos playing 

419
00:18:56.146 --> 00:18:59.161
when someone arrives 
on a landing page 

420
00:18:59.161 --> 00:19:01.980
and if you don't have 
visible controls to stop those, 

421
00:19:01.980 --> 00:19:06.208
it gets really disorienting 
for certain users. 

422
00:19:06.208 --> 00:19:07.639
You can see in this one, 

423
00:19:07.639 --> 00:19:11.120
there are links for 
closed captioning.

424
00:19:11.120 --> 00:19:13.037
There's links 
for speed control. 

425
00:19:13.037 --> 00:19:16.148
There's links 
for transcripts. 

426
00:19:16.148 --> 00:19:19.744
This video allows 
more control for the user 

427
00:19:19.744 --> 00:19:23.154
over this experience 
with the video. 

428
00:19:23.154 --> 00:19:26.045
This is an ugly slider. 
Sliders are actually 

429
00:19:26.045 --> 00:19:29.874
a big problem with 
achieving accessibility. 

430
00:19:29.874 --> 00:19:31.679
People love sliders at the
top of their websites or

431
00:19:31.679 --> 00:19:34.181
in the middle sometimes 
and they all have their 

432
00:19:34.181 --> 00:19:36.015
different challenges,
and actually there's 

433
00:19:36.015 --> 00:19:38.521
a lot of people who 
