434
00:19:38.521 --> 00:19:41.307
When developing a
slider, making a slide, 

435
00:19:41.307 --> 00:19:42.524
or putting one 
on your website, 

436
00:19:42.524 --> 00:19:44.956
keep some of these 
things in mind. 

437
00:19:44.956 --> 00:19:46.118
You want to have controls. 

438
00:19:46.118 --> 00:19:47.647
You want to have 
navigation elements. 

