00:20:22.159 --> 00:20:24.065
I'll give you my take. 

456
00:20:24.065 --> 00:20:26.647
You can easily add, 
for example, 

457
00:20:26.647 --> 00:20:28.042
on this one, 
create an image 

458
00:20:28.042 --> 00:20:30.320
that helps make your
images more informative

459
00:20:30.320 --> 00:20:33.039
to the user, is the
