597
00:26:28.158 --> 00:26:31.381
As you continue to hit Tab, 
it's hard to tell,

598
00:26:31.381 --> 00:26:32.589
but it went up 
to their Facebook. 

599
00:26:32.589 --> 00:26:34.516
It went up to 
the very top 

600
00:26:34.516 --> 00:26:36.374
of the main bar 
at the top 

