00:26:36.374 --> 00:26:39.558
then Twitter and then 
through all their social icons. 

602
00:26:39.558 --> 00:26:41.615
Then it moves to their logo 

603
00:26:41.615 --> 00:26:44.407
which means their main website, 
you know, home.

604
00:26:44.407 --> 00:26:48.884
About, brands, 
you see as it's indicating, 

605
00:26:48.884 --> 00:26:52.107
you can see the square 
is moving along with me 

606
00:26:52.107 --> 00:26:53.750
and I can choose that. 

607
00:26:53.750 --> 00:26:55.360
If I was consulting for Unilever,

