693
00:30:51.947 --> 00:30:57.243
Make the capital case like that. 
It helps differentiate the letters. 

694
00:30:57.243 --> 00:31:00.000
It makes it a little easier to read.

695
00:31:01.600 --> 00:31:05.614
Okay. Let's see here... 

696
00:31:05.614 --> 00:31:07.796
Let's continue on 
and the last thing 

697
00:31:07.796 --> 00:31:11.808
with button accessibility is, 
or link accessibility for this case, 

698
00:31:11.808 --> 00:31:14.786
the left one has 
no information as well. 

699
00:31:14.786 --> 00:31:16.960
For information on 
device independence, click here.

700
00:31:16.960 --> 00:31:18.995
"Click here", you see a lot,
people put that, 

