00:31:25.432 --> 00:31:28.327
and they know that it's about 
device independence 

705
00:31:28.327 --> 00:31:29.826
is what they're clicking on. 

706
00:31:29.826 --> 00:31:31.069
They know where it's 
going to be going. 

707
00:31:31.069 --> 00:31:33.032
That's true with links 
